Usage: deletePlaceBlockage [-help] [-all  | -type {hard soft partial macroOnly}] [-all  | <obs_name>]

-help                                   # Prints out the command usage
<obs_name>                              # blockage name (list, required)
-all                                    # delete all kinds of obstructions
                                        # (bool, required)
-type {hard soft partial macroOnly}     # delete all obstruction of this type
                                        # (enum, required)